title: Buffy the Vampire Slayer Season Nine 025 (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.



Buffy the Vampire Slayer Season 9 #25

By:   	Andrew Chambliss, Dexter Vines, Georges Jeanty, Michelle Madsen, Phil Noto	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Action-Adventure, Horror
Series:   	Buffy the Vampire Slayer
Publisher:   	Dark Horse	
Pub. Date:  	September 11, 2013
Format:         CBZ

Buffy can't ever just be a vampire Slayer, can she? Always, the world seems to want more, and as the lives of her loved ones are threatened, Buffy shows why she is the Chosen One. Whatever is thrust upon her, she can handle it! Er . . . sometimes with a little help from her friends.

* Executive produced by Joss Whedon!
